---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Florida Lawn Network - Your Lawn Care Connection"
  description="Learn about Florida Lawn Network's mission to connect homeowners with top-rated lawn care professionals in their area."
>
  <div class="bg-primary-800 py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-0">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl">
          About Florida Lawn Network
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-primary-100">
          Connecting homeowners with trusted lawn care professionals since 2024
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:py-16 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Our story section -->
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Our Story
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
          Florida Lawn Network was founded with a simple mission: to make finding reliable lawn care services as easy as possible. We recognized the frustration many homeowners face when trying to find trustworthy professionals to maintain their outdoor spaces.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
          What began as a small directory in Austin, Texas has grown into a comprehensive platform connecting homeowners with top-rated lawn care providers across the country. Our passion for creating beautiful outdoor spaces drives everything we do.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
          Today, we're proud to have helped thousands of homeowners transform their lawns and gardens into stunning outdoor retreats, while also supporting the growth of local lawn care businesses in communities nationwide.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 lg:mt-0">
        <img 
          class="rounded-lg shadow-xl" 
          src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3279307/pexels-photo-3279307.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" 
          alt="Team working outdoors"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Our mission section -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-primary-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
      <div class="px-6 py-10 sm:px-10 sm:py-16">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Our Mission
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600">
            To create a seamless connection between homeowners and lawn care experts, fostering beautiful outdoor spaces and thriving local businesses.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
            <div class="inline-flex rounded-md shadow">
              <a
                href="/directory"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 transition"
              >
                Find Lawn Care Providers
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Values section -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Our Values
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-600">
          The principles that guide everything we do
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-500 text-white">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Trust & Reliability</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            We thoroughly vet all providers on our platform to ensure they meet our high standards of professionalism and service quality.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-500 text-white">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Community Focus</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            We support local businesses and strive to strengthen communities by connecting homeowners with nearby lawn care experts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-500 text-white">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Environmental Stewardship</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            We promote sustainable lawn care practices that protect our environment and create healthier outdoor spaces.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Team section -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Our Team
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-600">
          Passionate professionals dedicated to connecting you with the best lawn care services
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="relative">
            <img 
              class="h-48 w-48 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover" 
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2381069/pexels-photo-2381069.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" 
              alt="Team member"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full shadow-inner"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Sarah Johnson</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Founder & CEO</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="relative">
            <img 
              class="h-48 w-48 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover" 
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2182970/pexels-photo-2182970.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" 
              alt="Team member"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full shadow-inner"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Michael Chen</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Chief Operations Officer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="relative">
            <img 
              class="h-48 w-48 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover" 
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3799799/pexels-photo-3799799.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" 
              alt="Team member"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full shadow-inner"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Emily Rodriguez</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Head of Provider Relations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="relative">
            <img 
              class="h-48 w-48 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover" 
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1516680/pexels-photo-1516680.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" 
              alt="Team member"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full shadow-inner"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">David Thompson</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Lead Developer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Testimonials section -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
      <div class="px-6 py-10 sm:px-10 sm:py-16">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl text-center">
            What People Say About Us
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-accent-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                      <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
                    </svg>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
              <blockquote>
                <p class="text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
                  "Florida Lawn Network made finding a reliable lawn service incredibly easy. Within a day of submitting my request, I had three quotes from vetted professionals. I've been using the same provider for over a year now, and my lawn has never looked better."
                </p>
              </blockquote>
              <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 font-medium">Jessica K. - Homeowner</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-accent-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                      <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
                    </svg>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
              <blockquote>
                <p class="text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
                  "As a lawn care business owner, joining Florida Lawn Network was one of the best decisions I've made. The platform has connected me with numerous clients in my service area, helping my business grow steadily over the past two years."
                </p>
              </blockquote>
              <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 font-medium">Mark R. - Lawn Care Provider</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Join us CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-primary-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
      <div class="px-6 py-12 sm:px-10 sm:py-16">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl">
            Join the Florida Lawn Network Community
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-primary-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Whether you're a homeowner looking for lawn care services or a provider wanting to grow your business, Florida Lawn Network is here to help.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
            <a
              href="/directory"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-primary-700 bg-white hover:bg-primary-50 transition"
            >
              Find a Provider
            </a>
            <a
              href="/get-listed"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border border-white text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white hover:bg-primary-600 transition"
            >
              List Your Business
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>